",n(t.p,{children:"Terraform modules are the building blocks of scalable infrastructure. This guide covers creating reusable modules for the most common AWS infrastructure patterns."}),"
",n(t.h2,{id:"project-structure",children:n(t.a,{className:"anchor",href:"#project-structure",children:"Project Structure"})}),"
",n(t.pre,{children:n(t.code,{className:"language-text",children:"terraform/
├── modules/
